---
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
import BeeTrail from "../ui/BeeTrail.astro";
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="service-highlight final-cta-panel" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Final CTA</p>
      <h2>Start with the map. We'll help the rest of the forest make sense.</h2>
      <p>
        The Growth Audit is still the cleanest first step when the trail feels messy.
        It turns scattered signals into a written plan you can use with or without us.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <Button href="/contact/">Get a Growth Audit</Button>
        <Button href="/services/" variant="secondary">Explore Our Services</Button>
      </div>
      <BeeTrail />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
